dcterms:creator: F. Guerrini
dcterms:description: The SZ-taxi dataset records the traffic speed of 156 major roads in Luohu District, Shen Zhen from January 1 to January 31, 2015. The traffic data is aggregated every 15 minutes and includes the topology of the road network.
dcterms:title: SZ-taxi

dcterms:creator: J. Liu
W. Guan
dcterms:description: The Los-loop dataset collects the traffic speed of 207 highways in Los Angeles County from March 1 to March 7, 2012. The traffic data is aggregated every 5 minutes, and the topology of the road network is available.
dcterms:title: Los-loop
